        "image_2": "shopify://shop_images/pf-a3b1b39c--Priscillablanconegr.png",
        "content_1": "Morito Chocolates is proud to be a female-owned company based in Brooklyn, N.Y., crafting chocolate sticks and cups made with intention.",
        "content_2": "<p>We began with chocolate sticks — a simple, small-batch expression of vegan chocolate made with organic, gluten-free ingredients and a short, intentional ingredient list. As Morito grew, so did the format.</p><p>Today, our cups carry that same foundation forward, reimagined through layered textures and refined flavors. A cacao-driven confection designed to feel light, creamy, and clean — always balanced, always distinctive.</p>"
